{"id":437,"parent_id":429,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":437,"title":"Nehemiah 8","subtitle":"","short_title":"Neh.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 8"],[".studySummary",["i","Ezra reads and interprets the law of Moses to the people—They keep the Feast of Tabernacles."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.1","order":"02.17.008.32043"},["b","1"],"And all the people gathered themselves together as one man into the street that",["i","was"],"before the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"water gate"],"; and they spake unto",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Ezra"],"the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"scribe"],"to bring the book of the law of Moses, which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"had commanded to Israel."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.2","order":"02.17.008.32044"},["b","2"],"And Ezra the priest brought the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"law"],"before the congregation both of men and women, and all that could hear with understanding, upon the first day of the seventh month."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.3","order":"02.17.008.32045"},["b","3"],"And he read therein before the street that",["i","was"],"before the water gate from the morning until midday, before the men and the women, and those that could understand; and the ears of all the people",["i","were attentive"],"unto the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"book"],"of the law."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.4","order":"02.17.008.32046"},["b","4"],"And Ezra the scribe stood upon a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"pulpit"],"of wood, which they had made for the purpose; and beside him stood Mattithiah, and Shema, and Anaiah, and Urijah, and Hilkiah, and Maaseiah, on his right hand; and on his left hand, Pedaiah, and Mishael, and Malchiah, and Hashum, and Hashbadana, Zechariah,",["i","and"],"Meshullam."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.5","order":"02.17.008.32047"},["b","5"],"And Ezra opened the book in the sight of all the people; (for he was above all the people;) and when he opened it, all the people stood up:"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.6","order":"02.17.008.32048"},["b","6"],"And Ezra blessed the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", the great God. And all the people answered, Amen, Amen, with lifting up their hands: and they bowed their heads, and worshipped the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"with",["i","their"],"faces to the ground."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.7","order":"02.17.008.32049"},["b","7"],"Also Jeshua, and Bani, and Sherebiah, Jamin, Akkub, Shabbethai, Hodijah, Maaseiah, Kelita, Azariah, Jozabad, Hanan, Pelaiah, and the Levites, caused the people to understand the law: and the people",["i","stood"],"in their place."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.8","order":"02.17.008.32050"},["b","8"],"So they read in the book in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"law"],"of God",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"distinctly"],", and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"gave the sense"],", and caused",["i","them"],"to understand the reading."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.9","order":"02.17.008.32051"},["b","9"],"¶And Nehemiah, which",["i","is"],"the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"Tirshatha"],", and Ezra the priest the scribe, and the Levites that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"taught"],"the people, said unto all the people, This day",["i","is"],"holy unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God;",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"mourn"],"not, nor weep. For all the people",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_9d"},"wept"],", when they heard the words of the law."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.10","order":"02.17.008.32052"},["b","10"],"Then he said unto them, Go your way, eat the fat, and drink the sweet, and send",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"portions"],"unto them for whom nothing is prepared: for",["i","this"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"day"],["i","is"],"holy unto our Lord: neither be ye",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"sorry"],"; for the joy of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"is your",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_10d"},"strength"],"."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.11","order":"02.17.008.32053"},["b","11"],"So the Levites stilled all the people, saying, Hold your peace, for the day",["i","is"],"holy; neither be ye grieved."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.12","order":"02.17.008.32054"},["b","12"],"And all the people went their way to eat, and to drink, and to send portions, and to make great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"mirth"],", because they had",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"understood"],"the words that were declared unto them."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.13","order":"02.17.008.32055"},["b","13"],"¶And on the second day were gathered together the chief of the fathers of all the people, the priests, and the Levites, unto Ezra the scribe, even to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"understand"],"the words of the law."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.14","order":"02.17.008.32056"},["b","14"],"And they found written in the law which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"had commanded by Moses, that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"the"],"children of Israel should dwell in booths in the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"feast"],"of the seventh month:"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.15","order":"02.17.008.32057"},["b","15"],"And that they should publish and proclaim in all their cities, and in Jerusalem, saying, Go forth unto the mount, and fetch olive branches, and pine branches, and myrtle branches, and palm branches, and branches of thick trees, to make booths, as",["i","it is"],"written."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.16","order":"02.17.008.32058"},["b","16"],"¶So the people went forth, and brought",["i","them,"],"and made themselves booths, every one upon the roof of his house, and in their courts, and in the courts of the house of God, and in the street of the water gate, and in the street of the gate of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"Ephraim"],"."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.17","order":"02.17.008.32059"},["b","17"],"And all the congregation of them that were come again out of the captivity made",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"booths"],", and sat under the booths: for since the days of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"Jeshua"],"the son of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"Nun"],"unto that day had not the children of Israel done so. And there was very great gladness."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.18","order":"02.17.008.32060"},["b","18"],"Also day by day, from the first day unto the last day, he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"read"],"in the book of the law of God. And they kept the feast seven days; and on the eighth day",["i","was"],"a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"solemn assembly"],", according unto the manner."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.1a","order":"02.17.008.32061"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/neh/3.26"},"Neh. 3:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.1b","order":"02.17.008.32063"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezra/7.6"},"Ezra 7:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.1c","order":"02.17.008.32065"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scribe"},"TG Scribe"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.2a","order":"02.17.008.32067"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/31.11"},"Deut. 31:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.3a","order":"02.17.008.32069"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezra/7.10"},"Ezra 7:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.4a","order":"02.17.008.32071"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/2.7.7-8"},"Mosiah 2:7 (7–8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.8a","order":"02.17.008.32073"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scriptures-study-of"},"TG Scriptures, Study of"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.8b","order":"02.17.008.32075"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/4.13.13-14"},"Jacob 4:13 (13–14)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.8c","order":"02.17.008.32077"},["b","8c"],["span.small","IE"],"gave a commentary by the power of the Holy Ghost.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/1.2-5"},"Mosiah 1:2–5"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.9a","order":"02.17.008.32079"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/neh/7.65"},"Neh. 7:65"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.9b","order":"02.17.008.32081"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/preaching"},"TG Preaching"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.9c","order":"02.17.008.32083"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mourning"},"TG Mourning"],"."],["div",{"id":"9d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.9d","order":"02.17.008.32085"},["b","9d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/4.1.1-2"},"Mosiah 4:1 (1–2)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.10a","order":"02.17.008.32087"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/esth/9.19"},"Esth. 9:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.10b","order":"02.17.008.32089"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/59.12.12-16"},"D&C 59:12 (12–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.10c","order":"02.17.008.32091"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/4.15.15-16"},"2 Ne. 4:15 (15–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.10d","order":"02.17.008.32093"},["b","10d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/strength"},"TG Strength"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.12a","order":"02.17.008.32095"},["b","12a"],["span.small","OR"],"rejoicing.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/50.22.17-22"},"D&C 50:22 (17–22)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.12b","order":"02.17.008.32097"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/4.3"},"Mosiah 4:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.13a","order":"02.17.008.32099"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/study"},"TG Study"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.14a","order":"02.17.008.32101"},["b","14a"],"This is the characteristic tradition of the feast of tabernacles.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/23.43"},"Lev. 23:43"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.17.16-17"},"Neh. 8:17 (16–17)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.14b","order":"02.17.008.32103"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/14.16"},"Zech. 14:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.16a","order":"02.17.008.32105"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/neh/12.39"},"Neh. 12:39"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.17a","order":"02.17.008.32107"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.14"},"Neh. 8:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.17b","order":"02.17.008.32109"},["b","17b"],["span.small","OR"],"Joshua."],["div",{"id":"17c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.17c","order":"02.17.008.32111"},["b","17c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/33.11"},"Ex. 33:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.28"},"Num. 11:28"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/16.34"},"1 Kgs. 16:34"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.18a","order":"02.17.008.32113"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.43.43-44"},"D&C 84:43 (43–44)"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.18b","order":"02.17.008.32115"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/solemn-assembly"},"TG Solemn Assembly"],"."]]}
